node.text: Jesus is sick of your shit. I’m not disrespecting you. You are disrespecting others by not wearing a mask and you’re disrespecting Christ by making it about him. How many more batshit crazy anti maskers do you need to read about dying before y’all give up? Also, if it’s your body and your choice to get vaccinated or wear a mask, then it’s mine to get an abortion. Right?? Right?! Last I checked, a pregnancy can’t infect others and kill people. 😳

Also, if it’s your body and your choice to get vaccinated or wear a mask, then it’s mine to get an abortion. Right?? Right?! Last I checked, a pregnancy can’t infect others and kill people. 😳
